\textbf{Huckel's Rule for Aromaticity:}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Cyclic, planar molecule
    \item Fully conjugated π \pi π -system
    \item Contains 4n+2 π \pi π electrons (n=0,1,2...)
\end{itemize}

